title: Good Omens (Amazon TV series) Review
author: Vassals of Kingsgrave
comment: I almost feel like Satan would have been more effective, if they had just went with "Benedict Cumberbatch in a suit", rather than the generic CG monster thing.  Having Satan being the "CEO of Hell" fits with the whole Heaven and Hell being a bureaucratic nightmare theme, and gives a bit more to Tempt Adam with.

description:
The Vassals discuss the new Amazon TV show and the cult fantasy book by Terry Pratchett and Neil Gaiman on which it was based.

Aftershow at 1hr 8m.

Hosts – Bina007, Adam/DrownedSnow, Dana/Taindana, Michal/Inkasrain, Jock/Munrock2 and Paul/SerDinnerRoll.
